79:T513,Looking for a **one-way drop taxi in Pudukkottai**? OneWayTaxi.ai offers the most affordable one-way drop taxi service from Pudukkottai, Tamil Nadu. Unlike traditional round-trip taxis where you pay for the driver's return journey, our drop taxi model charges you only for the distance you actually travel — **saving up to 40%** on your fare compared to competitors.

### Why Book Our Pudukkottai Drop Taxi?
Our Pudukkottai drop taxi fleet includes **Mini/Hatchbacks (₹13/km)**, Sedans like Swift Dzire and Toyota Etios (₹14/km), SUVs (₹19/km), and premium Innova Crysta (₹22/km). Every vehicle is air-conditioned, GPS-tracked, and regularly serviced for your comfort and safety.

### Popular Routes
Popular one-way drop taxi routes from Pudukkottai: Pudukkottai to Trichy (55 km, ~₹770), Pudukkottai to Thanjavur (58 km, ~₹812), Pudukkottai to Madurai (120 km, ~₹1680). Whether you're traveling for business, family visits, medical appointments, or pilgrimage, our Pudukkottai drop taxi service ensures a comfortable, reliable, and budget-friendly journey. All fares are inclusive of driver bata (allowance), toll charges, inter-state permits, and GST — what you see is what you pay, with absolutely zero hidden charges. Book your Pudukkottai drop taxi now online or call us 24/7.68:["$","section",null,{"className":"py-12 bg-white","aria-label":"Service description","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg prose-teal max-w-none","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-lg whitespace-pre-line markdown-content","children":"$79"}]}]}]}]
