6f:["$","$L98",null,{"districtName":"Pudukkottai","serviceLabel":"Drop Taxi","faqs":[{"question":"What is the starting fare for drop taxi in Pudukkottai?","answer":"The starting fare for drop taxi in Pudukkottai is ₹13/km for a hatchback. Sedan rates start at ₹14/km, SUV at ₹14/km, and Innova Crysta at ₹14/km. All fares include driver allowance, toll charges, and GST with no hidden costs."},{"question":"How do I book a drop taxi from Pudukkottai?","answer":"You can book a drop taxi from Pudukkottai instantly on OneWayTaxi.ai. Simply enter your pickup location, destination, date, and time. You'll get an instant fare estimate. You can also call us 24/7 at +91 81244 76010 for immediate booking."},{"question":"Is drop taxi from Pudukkottai available 24/7?","answer":"Yes, our drop taxi from Pudukkottai is available 24 hours a day, 7 days a week — including holidays and late nights. You can book at any time through our website or by calling our support team."},{"question":"What types of vehicles are available for drop taxi in Pudukkottai?","answer":"We offer 5 vehicle types for drop taxi in Pudukkottai: Mini/Hatchback (4 seats, ₹13/km), Sedan like Etios/Dzire (4 seats, ₹14/km), SUV/Innova (7 seats, ₹14/km), Innova Crysta (7 seats, ₹14/km), and Tempo Traveller (12 seats, ₹19/km)."},{"question":"Are there any hidden charges for Pudukkottai drop taxi?","answer":"No, absolutely not. Our Pudukkottai drop taxi fares are fully transparent and include all costs — driver bata, toll charges, permit fees, and GST. The fare you see at booking is the fare you pay. There are no surge charges, no night charges, and no return-trip charges."},{"question":"What is the fare from Pudukkottai to Trichy by drop taxi?","answer":"The drop taxi fare from Pudukkottai to Trichy starts at approximately ₹770 for a hatchback. The distance is about 55 km. Sedan fare would be around ₹770, and SUV around ₹770. Book now for exact pricing."},{"question":"Why is one-way drop taxi cheaper than round-trip in Pudukkottai?","answer":"With a round-trip taxi, you pay for the driver's return journey even though you only travel one way. Our Pudukkottai drop taxi eliminates this inefficiency — you pay only for the distance YOU travel. This saves you up to 40% compared to round-trip fares. We match return rides for our drivers, making it economical for everyone."},{"question":"Is it safe to book drop taxi in Pudukkottai with OneWayTaxi.ai?","answer":"Absolutely. All our Pudukkottai drop taxi drivers are professionally trained, background-verified, and carry valid licenses. Our vehicles are GPS-tracked in real-time, regularly serviced, and fully insured. We have served over 50,000 happy customers across South India with a 4.8-star average rating."},{"question":"What payment methods are accepted for Pudukkottai drop taxi?","answer":"We accept multiple payment methods for Pudukkottai drop taxi: Cash, UPI (Google Pay, PhonePe, Paytm), credit cards, debit cards, and net banking. You can pay the driver directly in cash or via UPI at the end of your trip. No advance payment is required for booking."},{"question":"Can I cancel my Pudukkottai drop taxi booking?","answer":"Yes, you can cancel your Pudukkottai drop taxi booking free of charge up to 2 hours before the scheduled pickup time. Cancellations within 2 hours may attract a nominal cancellation fee. Contact our 24/7 support at +91 81244 76010 for cancellations or rescheduling."},{"question":"How much does a taxi from Pudukkottai to Thanjavur cost?","answer":"A one-way taxi from Pudukkottai to Thanjavur costs approximately ₹812 for a hatchback (58 km). Sedan fare: ~₹812, SUV: ~₹1102. All fares include toll, driver bata, and GST."}]}]
